Package: IDEFICS.scalc
Type: Package
Title: Scoring Tools for Anthropometric and Metabolic Parameters in Children
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Andreas", "Mändle",
      email = "maendle@leibniz-bips.de",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    ),
    person(
      "Zülal", "Bekerecioglu",
      role = c("ctb")
      )
  )
Description: Provides tools to compute standardized percentiles and z-scores for anthropometric
    and metabolic parameters in children, based on age-, sex-, and height-specific reference data
    from the IDEFICS study. Supports computation of a composite Metabolic Syndrome (MetS) score
    and associated action levels for child health monitoring.
